Data Fields

UINT32 m_free_id

Detailed Description

Structure for device information about dynamic characteristics of the data store.

Field Documentation

UINT32 SyncMLDynamicProps::m_free_id
 

Specifies the number of free item identifiers available for adding new items to the datastore. Corresponds to the FreeID element in the SyncML Meta-Information DTD.

UINT32 SyncMLDynamicProps::m_free_mem
 

Specifies the amount of free memory, in bytes, available in the local datastore. Corresponds to the FreeMem element in the SyncML Meta-Information DTD.
